text: Nº3 is the third studio album by alternative rock band Dot Hacker. The album was released on January 20, 2017 on ORG Music label. The album cover art was created by Josh Klinghoffer although it was not originally designed for this purpose. == Track listing == == Personnel == Dot Hacker * Josh Klinghoffer – lead vocals, guitar, keyboards, synthesizers * Clint Walsh – guitar, backing vocals, synthesizers * Jonathan Hischke – bass guitar * Eric Gardner – drums == References == Category:2017 albums Category:Dot Hacker albums
title: Nº3
